greenmirror.commands

Class FlushCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • greenmirror.Command
      • greenmirror.commands.FlushCommand

  • public class FlushCommand
extends Command
    The command that tells the visualizer to create a new sub-queue of animations, meaning all upcoming animations will be played after the current sub-queue. This command is sent to the server.
    Values sent:
    variabletypedescription
    delay doublethe delay that is added after the previous animations
    Author:
    Karim El Assal
    See Also:
    FlushCommandHandler
